This document outlines performance criteria for Ted Cinema application

BASE_USER=50

1. Stress test movie details page with
   User Pool = BASE_USER
   Response Time = no more than 2 seconds
   Test Execution Duration = 24 hours
   Memory Usage = no more than 4 GB
   Garbage Collection = no more than 10 cycles
   
2. Stress test seat booking page with
   User Pool = BASE_USER/2
   Response Time = no more than 2 seconds
   Test Execution Duration = 24 hours
   Memory Usage = no more than 4 GB
   Garbage Collection = no more than 10 cycles
